Package: SternBrocot
Type: Package
Title: Approximation of Real Numbers as Rational Fractions Using the Stern-Brocot Tree
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-01-22
Authors@R: person(
    "Brian",
    "McAuliff Mulloy", 
    email = "brian@homeymusic.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Brian McAuliff Mulloy <brian@homeymusic.com>
Description: Provides tools for approximating real numbers as rational fractions 
    using the Stern-Brocot tree. Includes functions for precise approximations 
    with configurable uncertainty bounds and metadata about the approximation process.
